%% dart-metaflac layered module architecture
flowchart TD
    subgraph CLI["CLI  —  bin/metaflac.dart"]
        cli["Command-line interface\nMetaflacCommandRunner / legacy flag parser"]
    end

    subgraph API["API Layer  —  api/"]
        api["High-level convenience functions\nreadFlacMetadata · transformFlac"]
    end

    subgraph TRANSFORM["Transform Layer  —  transform/"]
        transform["FlacTransformer · StreamRewriter\nFlacTransformPlan"]
    end

    subgraph EDIT["Edit Layer  —  edit/"]
        edit["FlacMetadataEditor · MetadataMutation\nPaddingStrategy"]
    end

    subgraph MODEL["Model Layer  —  model/"]
        model["FlacMetadataDocument · VorbisComments\nStreamInfoBlock · PictureBlock"]
    end

    subgraph BINARY["Binary Layer  —  binary/"]
        binary["FlacParser · FlacSerializer\nByteReader · ByteWriter"]
    end

    subgraph IO["IO Layer  —  io/  ❨dart:io❩"]
        io["FlacFileEditor · AtomicWriter\nModTimePreserver"]
    end

    CLI     --> API
    API     --> TRANSFORM
    API     --> EDIT
    TRANSFORM --> EDIT
    EDIT    --> MODEL
    MODEL   --> BINARY

    IO -. "file read / write\n(dart:io adapter)" .-> TRANSFORM
    IO -. uses .-> BINARY
